reviewText: Of you were to give a group of 14 year old kids a video camera and a children's book as a script, they would produce a better more enjoyable movie than this.  If someone gives you a copy, use it as a coaster. If for some odd reason you must watch this steaming pile, do not pay more than 10 cents with free shipping. I paid $3 at goodwill and I feel ripped off.
